Description

Mood Meter is a user-friendly tool designed to help users express and monitor their emotions. The application features:

- A user-selectable mood meter with six emotions (Happy, Neutral, Sad, Angry, Excited, Fearful)
- Corresponding emojis to visually represent the chosen mood
- Inspirational messages displayed randomly every 5 seconds
- A pop-up message box providing guidance based on the selected mood

Features

- Interactive mood selection buttons
- Emojis representing different emotions
- Random inspirational quotes
- Customizable fonts, colors, and background

Requirements

- Python 3.x
- Tkinter library
- Random library


Code Highlights

- Utilizes Tkinter for GUI design
- Employs Python's random library for inspirational quotes
- Demonstrates simple event-driven programming with button commands
